                        (vermilion) ornamental bands; geometric motifs.</decoNote>
                     <decoNote type="frame" xml:id="d3">
                        <locus target="#21vb">21vb</locus>: simple and short, coloured (yellow,
                        black) ornamental bands; geometric motifs.</decoNote>
                     <decoNote type="frame" xml:id="d4">
                        <locus target="#108r">108r</locus> (incipit of the Gospel of John):
                        elaborate coloured (vermilion, yellow, black) ornamental band with three
                        lateral extensions reaching the bottom and connected by a horizontal band;
                        geometric motifs.</decoNote>
