               <provenance>According to Additio 1, priest (qasis ) Tasfā
                     Mikāʾel and priest Walda Gabǝr commissioned the Ms. They are also mentioned
                     together with “the children of deacon Nǝwāya Māryām” in the supplication
                     formula on 39va, and with “the children of Mäḥarä
                     Krǝstos” and “the children of Māḥleta Mikāʾel” in the concluding supplication
                     formula on 142ra.</provenance></history>
